title: Grateful Dead Live at San Antonio Civic Auditorium on 1972-11-26
description:
Set I
Promised Land, Deal, Mexicali Blues, Sugaree, Black Throated Wind, Bird Song, Beat It On Down The Line, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Box Of Rain, El Paso, Big Railroad Blues, Around & Around, Casey Jones
Set II
Playin' In The Band, Brown Eyed Women, Jack Straw, Don't Ease Me In, Big River, Dark Star-> Me And Bobby McGee, Brokedown Palace, Sugar Magnolia, Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> One More Saturday Night
 
Comment
'Beer Barrel Polka' and 'Zippedy Doo Dah' tunings before B.E. Women
